title: S1 Ep13: ETs and the ECETI Ranch
itunes:title: ETs and the ECETI Ranch
description: James Gilliland has the most active unassuming ranch you have ever seen.  By day, it can be as serene as ever... or you could see government Blackhawk helicopters. By Night, You could see the stars,,, or the visitors that have come from them to visit you!  James joins Darkness Radio to tell the unusual tales of the ECETI Ranch on today's show, and you won't be disappointed!
